<div class="editsection" style="float:right;margin-left:5px;">[<a href="/web/20090108122922/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=DoomEDIT_Categorised_Key_Bindings_and_Mouse_Controls&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: DoomEDIT Keyboard and Mouse Bindings">edit</a>]</div><a name="DoomEDIT_Keyboard_and_Mouse_Bindings"></a><h2> DoomEDIT Keyboard and Mouse Bindings</h2>
<div class="editsection" style="float:right;margin-left:5px;">[<a href="/web/20090108122922/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=DoomEDIT_Categorised_Key_Bindings_and_Mouse_Controls&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: General Usage">edit</a>]</div><a name="General_Usage"></a><h3> General Usage </h3>
<dl><dd><table style="width:75%">

<tr>
<td style="width:30%">
</td><td style="width:20%">
</td><td style="width:50%">
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td> Show Game </td><td> <b>F2</b> </td><td> Switches to Game <sup>*</sup>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td> Preferences </td><td> <b>P</b> </td><td> Opens the Preferences Window
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td> Light Properties </td><td> <b>J</b> </td><td> Open light editor window
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td> File Open </td><td> <b>Ctrl+O</b> </td><td> Opens the File Open box
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td> File Save </td><td> <b>Ctrl+S</b> </td><td> Saves the map
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td> Next Leak Spot </td><td> <b>Ctrl+Shift+K</b> </td><td> Go to the next point in the leak trace
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td> Leak Spot </td><td> <b>Ctrl+Shift+L</b> </td><td> Go to the previous point in the leak trace
</td></tr></table></dd></dl>
<p><sup>* Use Alt+Tab to switch back to the editor.</sup>
</p>
<div class="editsection" style="float:right;margin-left:5px;">[<a href="/web/20090108122922/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=DoomEDIT_Categorised_Key_Bindings_and_Mouse_Controls&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Inspector Box">edit</a>]</div><a name="Inspector_Box"></a><h3> Inspector Box </h3>
<dl><dd><table style="width:75%">

<tr>
